It's kind of sad,
the change of seasons.

1077
01:27:49,062 --> 01:27:52,097
Remember those big parties
we used to have out here?

1078
01:27:52,098 --> 01:27:54,266
Yeah.

1079
01:27:54,267 --> 01:27:58,203
It's just a dry patch
of dirt now.

